text: The N709 or Khulna City Bypass is a National Highway in Bangladesh. It connects Khulna with Mongla via Khan Jahan Ali Bridge. ==Length== 27 kilometer. ==Junction and important places== * Afil Gate * Chingrikhali Bazar * Teligati * Arongghata * Bil Pabla * Khulna Jail * Zero Point * Mohammad Nagar * Khan Jahan Ali Bridge * Kudir Bottola ==References== Category:National Highways in Bangladesh
title: N709 (Bangladesh)
